{"tid":1943471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出夠街未玩夠未？","createTime":"2020-03-25T17:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T18:28:30.000Z","uid":303858,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"24a4c5ae0d6dcbe2424cb2b0204358763579ea07","tid":1943471,"uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:00:20.000Z","msg":"真係屌晒老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日開ig係咁見到啲人po自己去邊到玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行邊座山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食邊間餐廳<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀，依家每日確診個案幾廿宗咁上，唔排除有社區爆化，你班人唔驚架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學校停課改online learning, 公司改wfh原意係希望你地留係屋企，減少出街次數，等你地唔洗出咁多街，減低中武肺吧機會，你班人就好似冇放過假咁，日撚日都出街玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我停課停嚟把撚？唔洗wfh啦唔洗zoom上堂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，你出街要用口罩，大佬啲口罩好珍貴架，原來你通宵排、上網鬧快搶嘅個啲口罩係俾你攞嚟出街玩，咁不如啲口罩留返俾有需要嘅人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留返俾醫護啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾你攞嚟出街玩真係嘥撚晒<br />\n<br />\n最過份你班人口口聲聲話支持醫護罷工，結果一個二個走晒去出街玩，如果你咁好彩中咗武肺，你對唔對得住醫你嘅個班醫護？醫護已經好大壓力，你對唔對得住佢地？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪忍耐下都唔得？係咪要前功盡廢，武漢肺炎大爆發你班人先識驚，先肯留係屋企？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n乖啦，留係屋企啦，等武肺完咗，先再出街啦，好嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港嘅醫護人員，我衷心多謝你地係呢個時刻嘅付出，你地要加油，支持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8706803993504092c50091982b79449aa2ca9cc1","tid":1943471,"uid":262497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"日日講㗎係聽就會聽 啲撚樣係咁自私㗎啦"},{"pid":"26f6bdbdc2f4bb06214c70c93c6805d33b3809c1","tid":1943471,"uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:03:07.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n有啲堂要開cam 但係次次都見佢喺條街度<br />\n唔上堂都要出街係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62e015fdb58a8bbb6965b66c4a30095a14b4e7f","tid":1943471,"uid":119250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"果啲屢勸不聽嘅人中咗真係唔得可憐"},{"pid":"9b1a06196baddb2d5c5da455c9ee4af273d16561","tid":1943471,"uid":303858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d62e015fdb58a8bbb6965b66c4a30095a14b4e7f","tid":1943471,"uid":119250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"果啲屢勸不聽嘅人中咗真係唔得可憐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:16:54.000Z","msg":"我登啲醫護慘"},{"pid":"00a7c3e0413fa9e8c6332c321603bd5e4fb90235","tid":1943471,"uid":303858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26f6bdbdc2f4bb06214c70c93c6805d33b3809c1","tid":1943471,"uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:03:07.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n有啲堂要開cam 但係次次都見佢喺條街度<br />\n唔上堂都要出街係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T17:17:40.000Z","msg":"完全扭曲晒停課嘅意義"},{"pid":"68dc5f7ec1d43159ce37c7a46c4769703dac13bb","tid":1943471,"uid":88725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b1a06196baddb2d5c5da455c9ee4af273d16561","tid":1943471,"uid":303858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d62e015fdb58a8bbb6965b66c4a30095a14b4e7f","tid":1943471,"uid":119250,"like":0,"disl